    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-12-07T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-12-07T00:00:00-05:00" n="68"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d68">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">862.00/383: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in the Netherlands</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Garrett</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">The Hague</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-12-07">December 7,
                            1918</date>.<lb/>[Received December 8—3:42 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>5420. Dutch press Wolff telegram Berlin 6th: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>[“] Document by which ex-Crown Prince gives up rights to crown of Prussia
                            and imperial throne has been received Berlin. Reads as follows: <quote
                                rend="blockquote">
                                <p>‘I do hereby expressly resign now and for all time all claims to
                                    [the] crown of Prussia and [the] imperial crown which might fall
                                    to me either through abdication of His Majesty the Emperor and
                                    King or through any other right Given under our own hand and
                                    signature at Wieringen on December 1st, 1918. Wilhelm.’[”]</p>
                            </quote>
                        </p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>Paris informed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Garrett</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
